title: Sara Schaefer
description: Sara Schaefer (emmy winning blogger for Fallon, You Had to Be There podcast, comedy) is a delightful guest: hilarious, thoughtful and DARE I SAY EVEN MOVING. A great episode with a lot of laughs AND a lot of heart. Good lord, get into it already! It's so good!!!
